<h2 id="live-it-out">Live It Out</h2>
<p class="lead">Start Doing: commit to a step and live it out this week.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Pick two or three relationships, and commit to honoring those people above yourself. Ask your group for helpful ideas.</li>
  <li>Talk to your LifeGroups and LifeMissions pastor about opportunities for your group to connect locally.</li>
  <li>This week memorize <a href="https://www.bible.com/bible/111/joh.15.12-13.niv">John 15:12-13</a></li>
</ul>

